Package: com.evilgoldfish.lockglyphx
Name: LockGlyphX Beta (iOS 10)
Depends: firmware (>= 10.0), mobilesubstrate, preferenceloader, org.thebigboss.libcolorpicker (>= 1.1)
Provides: com.evilgoldfish.lockglyph
Conflicts: com.evilgoldfish.lockglyph
Version: 1.0~b3
Architecture: iphoneos-arm
Description: LockGlyph for iOS 10.
 Change Log
 + scanning animation respects color setting when using a custom theme
 + customizing Press Home To Unlock text doesn't hide Press Home To Open text after unlocking
 + moved glyph behind music controls
 + changed default position of glyph
 + fixed bug with ColorFlow notifications
 + Prefs: moved position settings to their own page
 + Prefs: theme list is faster and indicates if a theme has sound
 + Prefs: can choose to always use the Apple Pay sound instead of theme sounds
 + some other fixes I can't remember right now, optimizations and polish
